---
import ToolLayout from "../../layouts/ToolLayout.astro";

const title = 'Reverse Text';
const description = 'Reverse text online. Balikkan teks, kata, kalimat, atau baris dengan berbagai mode.';
const keywords = 'reverse text, reverse string, balik teks, reverse words, reverse sentences';
const bodyHtml = `<header class="d-flex align-items-center gap-3 mb-4"><div class="tool-icon" style="background:#f0f9ff;color:#0891b2;">Aa</div><div><h1 class="h3 mb-0">Reverse Text</h1><p class="text-muted small mb-0">Balikkan teks dengan berbagai mode: balik karakter, kata, kalimat, atau baris.</p></div></header>
<div class="row g-4"><div class="col-lg-6">
<div class="card shadow-sm border-0 p-3">
<div class="mb-3"><label class="form-label fw-semibold">Input</label><textarea id="textInput" class="form-control font-mono" rows="5" placeholder="Masukkan teks..." autofocus>Halo, apa kabar?
Selamat datang di WebApps!
Semoga harimu menyenangkan.</textarea></div>
<div class="mb-3"><label class="form-label fw-semibold">Mode</label>
<select id="modeSelect" class="form-select"><option value="chars">Balik Karakter</option><option value="words">Balik Kata</option><option value="lines">Balik Baris</option><option value="wordsChars">Balik Kata + Karakter</option></select></div>
<button id="btnReverse" class="btn btn-primary w-100">Reverse</button>
</div></div>
<div class="col-lg-6">
<div class="card shadow-sm border-0 p-3">
<div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center mb-2"><label class="form-label fw-semibold mb-0">Output</label><button id="btnCopy" class="btn btn-sm btn-outline-secondary">Copy</button></div>
<textarea id="outputArea" class="form-control font-mono" rows="8" readonly></textarea>
</div></div></div>
<div class="mt-4 p-3 rounded" style="background:var(--surface-soft);border:1px solid var(--border)"><h6 class="fw-bold">Tentang Reverse Text</h6><p class="small mb-1" style="line-height:1.6">Reverse text online untuk membalikkan urutan karakter, kata, atau baris dalam teks. Alat ini menyediakan berbagai mode reverse yang berguna untuk berbagai keperluan: membalik karakter (olahragA jadi Agarlaho), membalik kata ('saya suka coding' jadi 'coding suka saya'), membalik baris, dan membalik urutan huruf dalam setiap kata. Cukup tempelkan teks dan hasil akan ditampilkan secara instan.</p><p class="small mb-0" style="line-height:1.6">Fitur meliputi: reverse teks per karakter, reverse per kata (membalik urutan kata dalam kalimat), reverse per baris (membalik urutan baris dalam paragraf), reverse per kata secara internal (membalik huruf dalam setiap kata tanpa mengubah urutan kata), dan mode flip text (membalik teks secara vertikal). Setiap mode memiliki tombol copy untuk menyalin hasil dengan cepat.</p><p class="small mb-0 mt-2" style="line-height:1.6">Reverse text tool berguna untuk: membuat teks unik untuk username atau bio media sosial, menulis teka-teki atau kode sederhana, memeriksa pola simetri dalam teks, belajar tentang struktur kalimat dan kata, menguji readability teks yang dibalik, dan bersenang-senang dengan manipulasi teks. Alat ini bekerja sepenuhnya di browser Anda secara offline.</p></div>`;
const extraHtml = `
<div class="mt-3 pt-2 d-flex gap-2 justify-content-center align-items-center">
<span class="small text-muted me-2">Bagikan:</span>
<a href="https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?url=" onclick="this.href+=encodeURIComponent(location.href)" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm rounded-pill" title="Twitter/X">&nearr;</a>
<a href="https://www.linkedin.com/sharing/share-offsite/?url=" onclick="this.href+=encodeURIComponent(location.href)" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm rounded-pill" title="LinkedIn">in</a>
<a href="https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=" onclick="this.href+=encodeURIComponent(location.href)" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm rounded-pill" title="Facebook">f</a>
<a href="https://api.whatsapp.com/send?text=" onclick="this.href+=encodeURIComponent(location.href)" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm rounded-pill" title="WhatsApp">wa</a>
</div>
<div class="mt-4 pt-2"><div class="small fw-semibold mb-2 text-muted">Alat Terkait</div><div class="d-flex gap-2 flex-wrap"><a href="palindrome-checker" class="btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm rounded-pill">Palindrome Checker</a><a href="anagram-finder" class="btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm rounded-pill">Anagram Finder</a><a href="text-repeater" class="btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm rounded-pill">Text Repeater</a><a href="char-counter" class="btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm rounded-pill">Character Counter</a></div>`;
---

<ToolLayout
  title={title}
  description={description}
  keywords={keywords}
>

<Fragment set:html={bodyHtml} />
<Fragment set:html={extraHtml} />

</ToolLayout>

<style is:inline>
.saweria-float { position: fixed; bottom: 24px; right: 24px; z-index: 9999; background: #ff6b6b; color: #fff; border-radius: 50px; padding: 10px 20px 10px 16px; text-decoration: none; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(255,107,107,0.4); transition: all 0.3s ease; font-family: "Inter",sans-serif; }
.saweria-float:hover { transform: translateY(-3px); box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(255,107,107,0.6); color: #fff; }
.saweria-float svg { animation: pulse 1.5s ease infinite; }
@keyframes pulse { 0%, 100% { transform: scale(1); } 50% { transform: scale(1.15); } }
@media (max-width: 576px) { .saweria-float { bottom: 16px; right: 16px; padding: 8px 14px 8px 10px; font-size: 12px; } }
</style>

<script is:inline>
document.getElementById('year').textContent=new Date().getFullYear();
</script>

<script is:inline>
var inp=document.getElementById('textInput'),mode=document.getElementById('modeSelect'),out=document.getElementById('outputArea');
document.getElementById('btnReverse').addEventListener('click',function(){
  var t=inp.value,m=mode.value;
  if(m==='chars')out.value=t.split('').reverse().join('');
  else if(m==='words')out.value=t.split(/\\s+/).reverse().join(' ');
  else if(m==='lines')out.value=t.split('\\n').reverse().join('\\n');
  else if(m==='wordsChars')out.value=t.split(/\\s+/).reverse().map(function(w){return w.split('').reverse().join('')}).join(' ');
});
document.getElementById('btnCopy').addEventListener('click',function(){
  if(!out.value)return;var b=this;
  navigator.clipboard.writeText(out.value).then(function(){b.textContent='Copied!';setTimeout(function(){b.textContent='Copy'},1500)});
});
document.getElementById('btnReverse').click();
</script>

<a href="https://saweria.co/naufalrakha" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="saweria-float" title="Donasi via Saweria">
  <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M12 21.35l-1.45-1.32C5.4 15.36 2 12.28 2 8.5 2 5.42 4.42 3 7.5 3c1.74 0 3.41.81 4.5 2.09C13.09 3.81 14.76 3 16.5 3 19.58 3 22 5.42 22 8.5c0 3.78-3.4 6.86-8.55 11.54L12 21.35z"/></svg>
  <span>Donasi</span>
</a>
<button class="dark-float btn btn-sm" title="Toggle dark mode" style="position:fixed;bottom:80px;right:24px;z-index:9998;width:44px;height:44px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--accent);color:#fff;border:none;font-size:1.3rem;box-shadow:0 4px 15px rgba(99,102,241,0.4);transition:all 0.3s ease;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;line-height:1;" onmouseover="this.style.transform='translateY(-3px)'" onmouseout="this.style.transform=''"></button>